data.description: Located conveniently to Robins AFB and downtown Warner Robins near the medical center, this home would be a great for a DIY team or investor. The home has all original hardwood flooring in the main living space and all 3 bedrooms.  Newer roof (Dec 2021) and all windows were replaced in 2007. Upon entering the home, there is a large area for a workout space, small business, or hobby/craft room to name a few. The property sits on just under 1/3 acre with a metal storage shed and 12x16 utility workshop. Come check this home out at a great price point!
